    "content": "<p>If you manage to land Neptune's trident Scatter symbol four times in Neptune's Fortune Megaways, you'll get 10 Free Spins. Land it five times, and you'll be gifted with a dozen Free Spins! And if you're really killing it and hit six Scatters, you'll receive a whopping 15 Free Spins. During these spins, low-value symbols are eliminated, and Wilds continue to keep us on the edge of our seats with their multiplier potential. Now that's what we call a great catch!</p>"
